        p April 2015: The Goods and Services Tax (GST) in Malaysia brought about a change in retailing, making it a legal requirement to issue receipts with every purchase. Larger retailers would whether the change just fine, but small business with little formal procedures would be particularly affected. Heavy accounting software would not be suitable for these small traders and GiveReceipt sought to arrive in time to plug that gap.

