        h3 Creating an identity
        p Professional accounting software is usually very staid. GiveReceipt aims to be more accessible, especially for small sole-traders. The name itself is comparatively informal, and we visuals that worked alongside that. 
        
        p If we were to pare a physical POS ribbon receipt down to its essence, we’d have a few ingredients: its form factor, the perforated edge caused my the blade, the light GSM of the stock. The perforation and aspect is something we could take forward as the basis for the identity. We're still dealing with money so the bright teal is grounded with sensible dark grey/white.

